# Title: Remote Service Activity via SVCCTL Named Pipe
# Author: Samir Bousseaden
# Date: 2019-04-03
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects remote service activity via remote access to the svcctl named pipe
# MITRE Tactic: Lateral Movement
# Tags: attack.lateral-movement, attack.persistence, attack.t1021.002
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/builtin/security/win_security_svcctl_remote_service.yml

AccessList="*WriteData*" EventID=5145 RelativeTargetName="svcctl" ShareName="\\\\\*\\IPC$"